<p style="text-align: center;">Eastern Europe Guardian Bear (&quot;Wojtek&quot;)</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">status: ok</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">California Guardian Bear (&quot;Fuerza&quot;)</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">status: recalled, pending reassignment</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Due to events outside of our organization's control</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">California Guardian Bear (&quot;Fuerza&quot;) has been relocated to our Headquarters</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">As international issues continue to increase in frequency</p>
